# Guest tools so ArchonSync behaves well inside virtual machines (display
# sizing, clipboard, smoother graphics). Harmless on real hardware — each one's
# service only activates under its matching hypervisor.
# VMware (incl. Fusion on Intel Macs):
open-vm-tools-desktop
xserver-xorg-video-vmware
# QEMU/KVM + Spice:
spice-vdagent
qemu-guest-agent
# (VirtualBox users install Guest Additions from the VirtualBox "Devices" menu;
# Debian trixie has no separate guest-x11 package to ship here.)
